adnoc_activity: Vessel released from shipping and sailed to MZP anchorage to berth on 26 Jan 2026 as requested by SCT.

MWS Sail away certificate was received Bushra Cast off MZP
Bushra Dropped anchor at Al Ghallan Anchorage waiting for Berth
MMT team travelled from Mina Port to AGI for TR No. 1 offloading
Bushra Berthed alongside West RoRo Berth No. 3 at AGI
J62 arrived to AGI with Lifting clamps for TR No. 1 offloading
Bushra dropped anchor at MZP anchorage waiting for berth
